821
01:13:51,920 --> 01:13:58,760
important point about strategy, which is 
intrinsically strategy has no business value.  

822
01:13:58,760 --> 01:14:08,640
It's basically a document with a few words. And I 
think it starts accumulating value as you generate  

823
01:14:08,640 --> 01:14:15,320
business impact and results. And that happens 
when you actually test strategy with execution. 

824
01:14:15,320 --> 01:14:22,320
And so ultimately any strategy is only as 
good as the results it produces. And so  

825
01:14:22,320 --> 01:14:27,120
one has to have the intellectual honesty, and 
the humility, and the courage to say when it's  

826
01:14:27,120 --> 01:14:32,000
working and when it's not. And sometimes what 
happens is parts of your strategy might work,  

827
01:14:32,000 --> 01:14:38,240
parts might not, and you have to pivot away 
from some and double down on some. But I do  

828
01:14:38,240 --> 01:14:44,400
think there's that evaluation that's really 
critical and testing strategy with execution.

829
01:14:44,400 --> 01:14:51,440
Such a great point. Just a strategy sitting there 
