01:15:13,160 --> 01:15:20,080
strong hypothesis, basically to start learning 
if this is the right path. And so I love that  

835
01:15:20,080 --> 01:15:24,960
your approach is like this middle ground 
between give it real time, but don't spend  

836
01:15:25,480 --> 01:15:30,920
three, four or five months working on this one 
document that just maybe one day you'll use.

837
01:15:30,920 --> 01:15:34,320
Exactly.
And there is room for a six-month process,  

