912
01:22:21,400 --> 01:22:25,720
but let's give us opportunity to think big. And 
oftentimes the biggest ideas come out of that.  

913
01:22:25,720 --> 01:22:30,640
So I love it's giving space for both types of 
thinking, thinking bigger and thinking long term. 

914
01:22:30,640 --> 01:22:35,240
Anything else about these two methods that 
might be interesting to share? Otherwise,  

