01:22:56,640 --> 01:23:04,120
satisfying processes to go through in the end. 
So once you get to the end, they're incredibly  

921
01:23:04,120 --> 01:23:11,080
deeply satisfying. But with anything in life 
that is very deeply satisfying at the end,  

922
01:23:11,080 --> 01:23:15,480
they have a ton of challenge, frustration, and 
